edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.file

Class CollectionFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.file.CollectionFile

  • public class CollectionFile
extends java.lang.Object
    The Collection file class stores objects to be saved/retrieved from a file. Any combination of the basic system contents can be stored/retrieved in this file, as well as additional user defined components. The basic system contents are systems (selected systems to be stored), environment (entire environment, consists of all components), settings, content (all content loaded into the environment), and execution data (data collected during an environment execution). Note: All classes stored in a file must be on a projects class path in order to retrieve the file successfully.
